Package gov.nasa.pds.registry.model.wrapper

Class ExtendedExtrinsicObject

java.lang.Object
gov.nasa.pds.registry.model.Identifiable
gov.nasa.pds.registry.model.RegistryObject
gov.nasa.pds.registry.model.ExtrinsicObject
gov.nasa.pds.registry.model.wrapper.ExtendedExtrinsicObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ExtendedExtrinsicObject extends ExtrinsicObject
Class leverages the Decorator Pattern by inheriting the functions of ExtrinsicObject through the ExtrinsicObjectDecorator class. Currently no methods are overridden, however, this provides that flexibility that should be a part of extending a class.
Author:
jpadams
